<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>nạsẖd sạwyrs</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- naṣībuki yā naf̊sī maẘlạki ạlạảmīn̊
 yuṭ̊ʿimuki daẘmaⁿạ ṭaʿāma ạl̊bāligẖīn̊
 laẙsa laki ạản̊ tā̊̉kulī
 ṭaʿāma miṣ̊ra ạlạảwãli

[V2]
 2- fuṭim̊ti ʿan̊ miṣ̊ra lima lạa tak̊tafī
 maḥ̊fūẓaẗaⁿ min̊ rabĩki ạl̊ḥif̊ẓa ạl̊kẖafī̃̊
 kunūzahu yub̊dī laki
 waḥubũhu yaḥ̊ṣuruki

[V3]
 3- yub̊dī laki fī ạl̊qaf̊ri maẘlạaki ạl̊ḥakīm̊
 ạản̊ taʿ̊rifīhi ạảnãhu ạlrãbũ ạlrãḥīm̊
 ḥiṣ̊nuⁿ waqudũwsuⁿ ṣabūr̊
 ại̹n̊ʿāmuhu kulã ạldũhūr̊

[V4]
 4- wāi̹n̊ ṭarīquki ṭawīlạaⁿ yūjadu
 fah̊wa kanas̊riⁿ ʿaz̊maki yujadĩdu
 rij̊lạki maʿ̊ ạảtẖ̊wābiki
 tub̊dī ạʿ̊tināʾa rabĩki

[V5]
 5- waʿin̊damā yā̊̉tī biki ḥubũ ạl̊qadīr̊
 limusẖ̊tahāki baẙti ạảbīnā ạl̊munīr̊
 tasẖ̊dīna lilrãbĩ ạl̊karīm̊
 tar̊nīmaẗa ạl̊ḥubĩ ạl̊ʿaẓīm̊</lyrics>
<title>nṣybk yạ nfsy mwlạk ạlạ̉myn</title>
</song>